title: Mont Rogneux
text: Mont Rogneux is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the Swiss <a href="Pennine%20Alps">Pennine Alps</a>, overlooking <a href="Liddes">Liddes</a> in the canton of <a href="Valais">Valais</a>. It is a mountain located north of the <a href="Petit%20Combin">Petit Combin</a> and <a href="Grand%20Combin">Grand Combin</a>. Facing the <a href="Verbier">Verbier</a> ski resort and neighbouring the Bruson lifts.
